reviewText: There were a few episodes I've never watched, but I haven't lived long enough to watch all episodes.. ;)
I love the little rascals very funny love it
Entire family enjoys Little Rascals very much. Thanks.
I bought as a Christmas gift for my husband & he has thoroughly enjoyed watching the DVD's as I can hear his laughter from another room in our home!!
Great memories, watch as a kid, now other kids get to enjoy.
I have so many memories when I was a kid, these are better kid movies than the one's they have now a days.

The Little Rascals are a classic. And don't forget bad with "Good" intentions. Nonetheless funny. This DVD had some of the very first episodes, with subtitles. Therefore you need to read out loud, if you have a child watching.
Did not like the silent episodes.  It was not entertaining for my grandson because he does not know how to read yet.  The rest of the episodes were OK.
Thought it was in color but it was black and white.  Little disappointing.
very happy with this vender and the shipment
